_Y_ rel symlink    _G_ chgrp        _E_xtension mark   _s_ort             _=_ pdiff
_S_ymlink          ^ ^              _F_ind marked      _._ toggle hydra   \\ flyspell
_r_sync            ^ ^              ^ ^                ^ ^                _?_ summary
